. 
. * figure out which drugs in our top group are otc
. 
. * we are using 2003 medicaid util data but 2005 drug product data
. * b/c 2003 drug product data was not available - should be very very similar
. * to comparable 2003 data - allows us to determine which ndcs are otc
. 
. * more recent version of drug product data is available on cms website at:
. * http://www.cms.hhs.gov/MedicaidDrugRebateProgram/09_DrugProdData.asp
. * can find utilization data at that same site
. 
. * this file aggregates ndcs to drug level to determine fraction of each drug'
> s
. * spending that are for otc ndcs
. 
